We've heard your feedback, and we’ve been working on updates to improve your experience with our app. Some of the changes included in this update are seeing all 30 days of transactions immediately, and quicker load times of account information.

We’ve also made a security update to help strengthen the safety of your information. Because of this, if you have Remember Me turned on, your settings will be removed, and you’ll have to re-enter your information. This applies to this release only. We apologize for any inconvenience.

Along with these updates, we’ve also made some minor bug fixes.

If you have any suggestions on ways we can improve your app experience, please leave feedback for us by logging into the app, tapping more in the navigation, and then selecting Feedback at the bottom. Thank you for being a member!
